title: Ohari
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Pizza, Indian, Italian, Buffet, Delivery, Take-out
description: Vegetarisches restaurant. Offers Indian food as well pizza and pasta. Many items offered vegan upon request. All-you-can-eat buffet on the 1st and 3rd weekend of the month Saturday from 5pm and Sunday from 1pm - until food is gone. Directions: direkt an der S-Bahn-Station Landwehr, Bus Nr. 25.
